This message contains the information needed to be able to generate a RINEX 3multi-GNSS observation file.This message contains pseudorange, Doppler, carrier phase, phase lock and signal qualityinformation for GNSS satellites once signals have been synchronized. This message supportsall active GNSS.The only difference between this version of the message and the previous version isthe addition of the version field.
